title: Butcher & Kurzmann 2006 The Big Misunderstanding
description: John Butcher & Christof Kurzmann ~ The Big Misunderstanding Between Hertz And MegaHertz ~ 2006 Potlatch P106. http://i5.imageban.ru/out/2017/06/25/fa98cbd15758e02389ed8caef9891bfc.jpg 1 Aume 2:55 2 Bee Space 2:54 3 Klafter 8:55 4 Redwood Second 7:18 5 Schilling 6:08 6 Seer 2:51 7 Shilling 8:40 8 Therblig 3:54 9 Thimbeful 2:21 Christof Kurzmann: electronics John Butcher: soprano & tenor saxophones ...The Misunderstanding offers nine rather short pieces -- four under three minutes, none longer than nine -- featuring tight, dense, rich improvisations. Kurzmann is extremely resourceful and Butcher engages him with what sounds like the thrill of discovery. In a year where Butcher followers have been extremely well treated already (Polwechsel's Archives of the North, the Contest of Pleasures' Albi Days), this album turns out to be another keeper. - Francois Couture, AMG
